          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Weatherizing Infrastructure in the North and Terrorism Emergency Readiness Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to develop and conduct a collective-response-to-terrorism exercise that includes managing cascading effects on critical infrastructure, such as an extreme cold-weather event caused by a polar vortex.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-07-10T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
